<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.851388>
    dc:description "FIG. 3. Map of Cuba and neighboring islets, plotting known locality records of three species of Heteroctenus Pocock, 1893: A. H. junceus (Herbst, 1800) (circles). B. H. garridoi (Armas, 1974), comb. nov. (squares); H. gibarae (Teruel, 2006), comb. nov. (crosses)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/851388/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

